title: Great except for one issue
text:
I use TikTok about everyday, it’s probably the app I spend the most time on and I’m not embarrassed to say that. TikTok is a great place to find comedic videos and images, communicating with others. Alongside this the app gives many ways to express yourself whether it’s with emojis, video effects, templates, to the millions of filters! TikTok is an overall amazing app, the only major issue I have with it is that it lacks a favorite button. The device I use TikTok on is an iPhone 13. I am unsure if there is an issue with my phone or the app but when I use the app it does not allow me to add videos to my favorites. There’s no button and I’ve tried clearing my cache updating the app countless times but nothing seems to work. 
 

Overall great app but please give me my favorites button. Thanks for reading and I’d love some feedback on this ♥️
